targetResourceId.Description: The fully qualified ID of the target resource that was changed

targetResourceType.Description: The namespace and type of the resource

changeType.Description: The type of change that was captured in the resource

changes.Description: A dictionary with changed property name as a key and the change details as the value

correlationId.Description: The ARM correlation ID of the change resource

timestamp.Description: The time the change(s) on the target resource ocurred

changesCount.Description: The number of changes this resource captures

previousResourceSnapshotId.Description: The GUID of the previous snapshot

newResourceSnapshotId.Description: The GUID of the new snapshot

propertyChangeType.Description: The type of change that occurred

changeCategory.Description: The entity that made the change

previousValue.Description: The target resource property value before the change

newValue.Description: The target resource property value after the change
